Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.60,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť, Gaigo-kun, odpusť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.00,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa preboha stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.00,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.28,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sme tam došli, bol už...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.48,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to niekto z Tancujúcich mečov?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:06.02,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne, ale žiaden človek, by toto nedokázal urobiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:12.63,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže to nebol Daigo-kun, však?\N Potom to muselo byť niečo iného...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.43,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to Daigo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.31,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzeral, ako démon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.32,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmenil sa na bieleho démona a roztrhal toho chlapa svojimi čeľusťami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.53,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Videla som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.71,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalo sa to pred mojimi očami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:43.85,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, takže sú aj iné miesta kam by Aoi,\N mohla ísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:48.24,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno... Áno... ďakujem veľmi pekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.58,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Banda príživníkov! \NOdporný pohreb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.48,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruším ten váš malý pohreb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.73,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si to za človeka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.73,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.31,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si ty kedy urobil pre mamu,\N keď trpela?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.29,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol si príliš zaneprázdnený golfom. \NJe to tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.62,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je pre teba tvoja práca oveľa dôležitejšia,\N ako my?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:21.74,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak potom ti všetko vezmem, aj tvoju drahocennú povesť!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.38,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej! \NČo to tam robíte!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:39.66,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To som ja Daigo. Daigo Yuuya,\N syn vášho šéfa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:43.67,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak máte nejaký problém, choďte to povedať môjmu starému!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.05,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.50,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stane sa naozaj démonom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:56.01,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmenil sa v bieleho démona.\N To si vravela, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.56,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Žeby to bola moc Byakko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.56,01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,59)}Poznámka: Byakko=Biely tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.51,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiež si to myslím.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.51,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.01,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to sila, ktorá vzniká na tomto svete, a je známa, ako Žltý drak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.48,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to obrovská sila, ktorá je v srdci všetkého živého.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:22.45,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorí sa že, tí ktorí sú obdarení touto mocou, \Ndržia svet vo svojich rukách.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.70,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby sa však moc Žltého Draka mohla prejaviť,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:29.06,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,musia sa ďalšie štyri sily, ktoré ho chránia spojiť:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:33.68,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiryuu, Suzaku, Gembu a Byakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:33.68,nm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,144)}Štyria Strážcovia \NKruhu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:34.95,nm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(478,320)}Seiryuu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:34.95,nm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(239,388)}Suzaku
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:34.95,nm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(397,96)}Gembu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.13,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto sila je známa ako Shijin\N{\c&HE3CF4F&}( Shijin=Štyri Božstvá)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:34.95,nm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,304)}Byakko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:41.02,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vraví sa, že majú moc držať temnotu pod svojou kontrolou a chránia Žltého Draka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:45.30,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa všetky štyri sily správne spoja...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.89,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,... tak na zemi zavládne mier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.33,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže to znamená, že Daigo-sama bol schopný vyvolať Byakko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.82,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.11,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaňte o ňom takto hovoriť!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:04.71,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýlite sa! \NTá vec nemohla byť Daigo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.30,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť!\N Odpusť, Daigo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.48,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to všetko, iba moja vina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.01,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Komaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.11,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Aua!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.02,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do pekla...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.54,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.30,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:43.80,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie sú, Tatsumi a Komaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.95,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu niekto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.94,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde to sakra som!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.77,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.40,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím vráť sa do dielne, Miroku-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.27,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa tu budeš takto prechádzať, môžu nastať problémy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:18.80,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Há?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.69,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To snáď nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.67,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde to sakra som?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.20,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, takže si sa prebral?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.42,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si...\NTy si ten chlap odvtedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.59,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to, že som tvojím dlžníkom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.99,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem kto si, ale ...ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.86,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kam máš namierené?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.47,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.52,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože, ten chlap s mečom \Ntu stále niekde sliedi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:52.15,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš si, že ho môžeš poraziť v stave, v akom si teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.27,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.03,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakajú ma priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.51,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám čas sa tu zdržiavať!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.18,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Požičiam si to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.15,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusti to, do frasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.13,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do riti, dedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.11,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to sakra, robíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:25.32,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Umrieť bez šance, \Nnie je povinnosťou človeka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.11,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.56,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo s tým mám robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.11,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.01,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni všetci ťa prijali, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.15,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj odporný otec nakoniec odišiel z práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.78,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy mu neodpustím.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.16,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie si ani povinný.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:03.56,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale dôležitejšie je, čo tvoje zranenia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.88,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nevládzem už vystáť môjho starého.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.55,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to takto pôjde ďalej, zabije ma, \Nako psa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.99,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ho, zabijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.99,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne, zabijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.00,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.06,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúbil si mi, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.23,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Však budeme vždy držať spolu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.32,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to sľub, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.61,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Držať spolu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:32.64,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.51,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme... spoločne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:39.86,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pôjdeme spoločne... na samé dno pekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.35,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Však? \NYuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.29,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zradca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.45,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:55.37,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť, neviem čo môžem\N pre teba urobiť,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:58.97,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,ale, zostanem pri tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.55,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som si to, dospel si k rovnakému záveru,\N že Doshin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:09.36,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne, predpokladajme, že padol do pazúrov\N Tancujúcich mečov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.26,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďalšia Hviezda osudu padla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.85,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Narutaki Togo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:21.47,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevinnosť, s jednoduchou nevinnosťou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.05,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.27,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:31.90,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do riti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.69,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otecko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.94,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.50,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otecko! Otecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.95,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy neodpustím odporným ľuďom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.78,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy im neodpustím!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.41,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypadni!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.91,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nie je ti zima, chlapček?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:17.41,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, no, čo sa deje, chlapček?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.03,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T... Ty malé hovno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.98,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevieš, kedy prestať, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.04,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno potrebuje odrezať dva, alebo tri prstíky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.18,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stačilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:28.95,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Há?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.44,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto do riti si?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.70,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naňho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:39.53,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hou... Houraiji Kyouichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:43.47,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui... Kamui Kyoshiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.68,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monštrum?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.31,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.52,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte raz... Ešte raz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.98,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte raz... Ešte raz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.05,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže ty si Daigo, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.38,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ty musíš byť nájomný samuraj Kabukicho, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.94,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Sakra! Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.95,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo? \NPovedz mi prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.58,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Proti čomu obraciaš svoj meč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.63,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Proti čomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.96,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomstiť sa za svojho otca?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:51.02,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dôvod prečo prehráš so svojím mečom, Kyouichi, \Nje že si príliš veríš.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.81,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.83,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj meč...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.81,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,... nebol zameraný na mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:09.05,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostal sa do správneho rytmu, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.38,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj, už je to oveľa príjemnejšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.60,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kruci, stratila som sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.07,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela som, že to nebude fungovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.90,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To sú...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:43.60,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oribe, udržujú bariérou, \Nnežiadúcich ľudí vonku, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.70,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,17 rokov...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:49.63,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To je príliš dlhá doba, pre nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:55.17,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No a teraz, späť do práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.21,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rezervná ochranná bariéra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.39,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vytvoril zaujímavú imitáciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.66,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.11,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On dokáže prelomiť bariéru majstra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:14.43,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, teraz to všetko začína byť logické...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.98,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez pochýb, naším nepriateľom je...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.03,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci sú tu.\N To nám mnoho uľahčuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.21,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to poslední vrahovia z Tancujúcich mečov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.20,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz pomstím mníchov z Dvadsiateho-ôsmeho súhvezdia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:33.57,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.60,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.81,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem bojovať! \NKomaki postaraj sa o Daiga-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.15,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.06,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Samota je tak bolestivá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.81,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola si tak osamelá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.07,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:12.12,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi! \NOdpusť mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.02,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem to urobiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.38,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem to urobiť.\N Jednoducho nemôžem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.60,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.39,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otvor, to som ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.87,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to naozaj také naliehavé?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.39,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, než bude príliš neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.95,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, asi nemám na výber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.37,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.19,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.99,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Magatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.44,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Héj!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.04,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehýbe sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:03.94,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je ako kameň, nehýbe sa ako kameň.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.87,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chladol kúsok po kúsku,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.43,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,až sa z neho stal kameň.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.98,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokázal som to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.96,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne som ho zabil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:20.63,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Už sa nebude hýbať, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.15,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.24,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Mýliš sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.92,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.09,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to nesprávne, Magatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.25,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol si všetko, čo som v živote mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.08,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydrž! \NOtvor oči!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.40,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun!\N Prosím ťa nemeň sa znovu na to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.74,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa! \NMýliš sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.83,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoločne... klesneme spolu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:53.57,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty a ja, pôjdeme do pekla spoločne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.18,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.06,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mení sa... To je zlé...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:03.73,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T... To je... premena v Byakkko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:04.99,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.67,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:12.63,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie zas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.00,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie zas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.40,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadiaľto, pán démonov.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.58,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, ten chlap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.22,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovec démonov?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.70,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vezmi si to na jeho hrob.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.70,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To je... Hyouraijiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.32,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty zasraný debil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.97,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odporné slová...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.64,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So mnou takto nebudeš rozprávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:44.16,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai-sama, budem si ťa chrániť!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.00,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Luk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.86,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Luk... Chcem svoj luk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.76,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.76,01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,66)}Poznámka: Hoshi=Hviezda
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.06,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.23,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-sama, Honzuihon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.23,01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(331,61)}Poznámka: Honzuihon=Zhodná formácia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.07,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.66,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zasiahni ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.42,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:52.55,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Daigo Yuuya... som...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.07,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha... Takže si Daigo-kun, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.54,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som Sakurai Komaki. Teší ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.54,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:05.46,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun! Daigo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.99,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:45.55,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak čo? Máte na neho krásne spomienky?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:49.25,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľutujete, že ste získali moc, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:53.15,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľutovať?\N Nepoznám to slovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.85,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.50,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte mi, to meškanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.22,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.78,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.27,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.96,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte stále žiješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:10.95,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, že som ťa sklamal, \Nale hrdina nikdy neumiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:13.06,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To ma teší.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:15.69,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tentoraz mi ponúkni trochu\N viacej zábavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:21.12,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezahrávaj sa so mnou, \Nty perverzná riť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.98,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosiahol neohrozené a neochvejné srdce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.03,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakoniec si ho našiel...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:30.03,Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
